description: Welcome to 20 F Street, a beautifully updated 2-bedroom, 1.5-bath single-family home nestled in the heart of South Boston's West Side. This modern residence offers a perfect blend of style, comfort, and convenience, just moments from public transportation, vibrant restaurants, and boutique shops. Step inside to discover open-concept living, where contemporary finishes and thoughtful design create an inviting space for both relaxing and entertaining. The sleek kitchen flows seamlessly into the dining and living areas, maximizing space and functionality. Outdoor living is a standout feature of this home, boasting a private patio, deck, and an incredible roof deck—all perfect for entertaining or unwinding while taking in stunning Boston skyline views. With its prime location and modern amenities, this home is the perfect city retreat.
